ame does not conform\")\n  }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1350, "output": 925, "cacheRead": 24576, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26851, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777793778984, "responseId": "resp_0c5ce33f54cdb1360169f6faf36e9c81a2866989059f590087"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_0deYSAi2IbWh8CuI1skBBJKJ|fc_0c5ce33f54cdb1360169f6faf95bd481a2acff70c77173c3d9", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1749 bytes to tests/src/com.typesafe.slick/slick_3/3.6.1/src/test/scala/com_typesafe_slick/slick_3/DatabaseConfigTest.scala"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777793787948}]}
